First Web Bundle
===============================================================================

This guide shows the minimal flow for producing static web assets from a configured browser project.

1. Build the WASM package
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

```sh
cd src/wasm
wasm-pack build --target web
cd ../..
```

2. Bundle the project
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

```sh
mech bundle-web examples/browser-dom-demo --out dist/browser-dom-demo
```

3. Serve the static output
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

```sh
python -m http.server 9000 -d dist/browser-dom-demo
```

Open:

```text
http://127.0.0.1:9000/
```

4. Static URL rule
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Static bundles must use relative URLs for Mech assets. Use `./pkg/...` and `./code/...`, not `/pkg/...` or `/code/...`.
